{"tid":1463650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"吊起核心暴力分子(公安/狗)遊街示眾啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:43.000Z","uid":61878,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"263c08da64c4f875956a9557085a420364c9795b","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"要最大化利用依件<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共公安送既禮物</span><br />\n係要將佢地變晒做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">&quot;人&quot;宣</span></strong></span><br />\n綁起佢示眾遊街<br />\n係佢身上貼晒<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;我是中國公安我是暴徒&quot;</span></strong></span><br />\n多國語言版<br />\n上晒國際頭版<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢本身帶晒武器就係想挑動暴力<br />\n有冇諗過個局就係佢表露咗自己公安嘅身份<br />\n然後啲狗(相信佢地今日都唔會帶任何證)帶頭打佢引大家係鏡頭前使用暴力<br />\n咁反送中就唔單止係&quot;香港人=中國暴徒&quot;<br />\n仲係&quot;香港人=國際暴徒&quot;<br />\n<br />\n順手叫大家簽埋依份<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">&lt;中國=恐怖分子&gt;</span></strong></span>既聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=f2a0e24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"93a15575295dc3b0717e6b64b1a42bec423ba024","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d0c15eae14970895d4a02c300d491eb8bc177162","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ccbef89448a0363927cef3a674e60cc0e85e3d35","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81a171d6d05cc27265f702fd21948a57771a40","tid":1463650,"uid":258246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"要塞唔係唔得<br />\n但要直接spin落個中國公安度<br />\n同啲旅客解釋返<br />\n如果佢地有去過示威地點<br />\n家陣check in好危險<br />\n中國派咗好多公安落嚟做嘢<br />\n要揾外國人做人質。<br />\n加拿大華為單嘢大家唔係唔記得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuaX5sa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuaX5sa.png&h=d1d8bd81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港班公安咁撚陰濕<br />\n已經想頭爆外國記者啦"},{"pid":"aa1f259fd04c8ea27c74aa1c96f8d1ec241aea25","tid":1463650,"uid":58826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"agree<br />\n<br />\n要&ldquo;多國&ldquo;語言先有用。要全世界嘅人都睇到"},{"pid":"fed93ef39e9c6f451e194cbaeab065f3057066fe","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"我是中國公安我是暴徒!!!"},{"pid":"2797dbcee2ea374e8d2ee42eeb57ed999c70c88f","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"我是中國公安我是廢青暴徒!!!!!"},{"pid":"a68cd3cf9ae8ec76fe60adfbf0a4ec4642ea46ac","tid":1463650,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客的話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"2b013e603ba2ef2e2223a279594fd4e43eb969ce","tid":1463650,"uid":61878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl